Promotion Final

First Leg [May 27]
Ramonense    2-2 Liberia
  [Warren Granados 68, Diego Lobo 83; Harold Miranda 53, Jose Humberto Ugarte 79]

Second Leg [Jun 3]
Liberia      2-1 Ramonense
  [Berny Canales 16, Harold Miranda 48; Warren Granados 71] 

